@startuml
scale 1.2

together {
    class EventSource
    note top of EventSource
    用来支持以下功能：
    <b><color:red>当property变更时生成事件，</color></b>
    <b><color:red>并触发你注册的监听器</color></b>
    end note
    interface Configuration
    note top of Configuration
     用来支持以下功能：
    <b><color:red>对property进行增删改查</color></b>
    end note
    abstract class AbstractConfiguration
    class ConcurrentMapConfiguration 
    class ConcurrentCompositeConfiguration {
        - List<AbstractConfiguration> configList
        - AbstractConfiguration overrideProperties;
        - AbstractConfiguration containerConfiguration;
    }
}
AbstractConfiguration .up.|> Configuration
AbstractConfiguration -up-|> EventSource
ConcurrentMapConfiguration -up-|> AbstractConfiguration
ConcurrentCompositeConfiguration -up-|> ConcurrentMapConfiguration

class ConfigurationManager
note top of ConfigurationManager
通过它，
<b><color:red>初始化配置对象，</color></b>
<b><color:red>提供将配置文件(本地、远程)添加</color></b>
<b><color:red>到configList中的方法</color></b>
end note
AbstractConfiguration -left-o ConfigurationManager

class DynamicPropertyFactory
note left of DynamicPropertyFactory
通过它，
<b><color:red>获取支持动态配置的property对象</color></b>
end note
interface DynamicPropertySupport
class ConfigurationBackedDynamicPropertySupportImpl
ConfigurationBackedDynamicPropertySupportImpl .up.|> DynamicPropertySupport
AbstractConfiguration -left-o ConfigurationBackedDynamicPropertySupportImpl
DynamicPropertySupport -right-o DynamicPropertyFactory


interface EurekaInstanceConfig
note top of EurekaInstanceConfig 
   当前实例身份的配置信息,
    即<b><color:red>我是谁？</color></b>
end note
abstract class AbstractInstanceConfig
abstract class PropertiesInstanceConfig
AbstractInstanceConfig .up.|> EurekaInstanceConfig
PropertiesInstanceConfig -up-|> AbstractInstanceConfig
DynamicPropertyFactory -down-o PropertiesInstanceConfig

interface EurekaClientConfig
note top of EurekaClientConfig
    一些影响当前实例和Eureka Server 
    交互行为的配置信息，
    即<b><color:red>和谁交互？怎么交互？</color></b>
end note
class DefaultEurekaClientConfig
DefaultEurekaClientConfig .up.|> EurekaClientConfig
DynamicPropertyFactory -down-o DefaultEurekaClientConfig

interface EurekaServerConfig
note top of EurekaServerConfig
    一些影响当前Eureka Server和客户端
    或对等节点交互行为的配置信息，
    即<b><color:red>怎么交互？</color></b>
end note
class DefaultEurekaServerConfig
DefaultEurekaServerConfig .up.|> EurekaServerConfig
DynamicPropertyFactory -down-o DefaultEurekaServerConfig


